metadata.name: Guardian 1 - Alis
metadata.description:
guardians

The inner child that keeps our shell alive, the one that keeps our sanity and guides our steps towards what we always wanted to be, the one that marks where we want to go, and who we go to when we need it most.

Alis - The one who protects

The one who bears the burden, the always smiling knight who gives everything for his loved ones even if he is hurt or will be.
